<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Named in honour of the Dipterist Dick Vockeroth (1928-2012), who already indicated on the labels that some specimens from Uganda probably belonged to a new species. The specific epithet should be treated as a noun in the genitive case.</paragraph>
